These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, pop, disco
1. the fan of folk is between the fan of pop and the fan of disco##2
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | disco | folk | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, 7up, coffee
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | coffee | tea | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, lizard, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the goldfish##2
3. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | fish | goldfish | lizard | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, apple, pomegranate, pumpkin
1. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating apple and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | pumpkin | apple | pomegranate | raspberry |

 #################################

 
