.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, fanta
1. the person drinking water is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water | hot-chocolate | fanta |

 